    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hi, InstantSearch is typed to expect the API client coming from `algoliasearch` or `algoliasearch/lite`, not from the package you used. You should be able to switch to one of those imports with no impact on your codebase:\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nimport { liteClient as algoliasearch } from 'algoliasearch/lite';\r\n// or\r\nimport { algoliasearch } from 'algoliasearch';\r\n```",
